content:
Create one or more rules that Service Cloud Voice can subscribe to and use to trigger real-time recommendations or auto-launched flows in Salesforce. 

To create a rule, click Rules in Amazon Connect. 
Click Create a rule | Contact lens. 
From the When dropdown, select A Contact Lens real-time analysis is available. 
Service Cloud Voice doesn't support Contact Lens Post-Call Analysis.

Add one or more conditions based on uttered keywords, sentiments, customer attributes, or other criteria. If you add multiple conditions, specify whether any or all conditions must be met.
Click Next and enter a descriptive name of the category.
Click Save and publish to review and save the rule.

A new rule applies only to contacts that occur after the rule is added.
title: Setting Up Amazon Connect Rules for Service Cloud Voice
